Package org.openehr.rm.data_types.quantity

Interface DvAbsoluteQuantity

All Superinterfaces:
org.openehr.base_foundation_types.Any, org.openehr.base_base_types.definitions.BasicDefinitions, DataValue, DvOrdered, DvQuantified, org.openehr.base_base_types.definitions.OpenehrDefinitions, org.openehr.base_foundation_types.primitive_types.Ordered
All Known Subinterfaces:
DvDate, DvDateTime, DvTemporal, DvTime
public interface DvAbsoluteQuantity extends DvQuantified
Abstract class defining the concept of quantified entities whose values are absolute with respect to an origin. Dates and Times are the main example.
